&lt;p&gt;&lt;span&gt;Liverpool University Hospitals are seeking to recruit an Assistant Domestic Manager for their Aintree site.&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;span&gt;As the Assistant Domestic Manager you will be responsible for managing the afternoon and weekend domestic service to ensure that cleaning is delivered to the Trust required standards&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;span&gt;You will manage a supervisory team and have daily contact with key stakeholders such as infection control and ward managers.&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;span&gt;Cleaning Management experience is an essential element for this role and experience within an healthcare environment would be beneficial. &lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;For further details / informal visits contact:&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;NameJacci Smith BradyJob titleAssistant Domestic ManagerTelephone number01515293274&lt;/p&gt;
